<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head', {
        title: '会话保持测试 - 负载均衡测试站点',
        extraCss: '<style>.session-container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; } .ua-value { font-size: 12px; }</style>'
    }) %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav', { active: 'session', serverIP: serverIP }) %>

    <div class="container session-container">
        <h1>
            <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'bar-chart-3', size: 22 }) %>
            会话保持测试结果
        </h1>

        <% if (sessionPersistent) { %>
            <div class="status-card status-card--success">
                <h3>
                    <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'check', size: 16 }) %>
                    会话保持成功
                </h3>
                <p>用户 <strong><%= username %></strong> 的会话正常保持，JSESSIONID: <code><%= sessionId %></code></p>
                <p>登录时间: <%= loginTime %></p>
            </div>
        <% } else { %>
            <div class="status-card status-card--danger">
                <h3>
                    <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'x', size: 16 }) %>
                    会话保持失败
                </h3>
                <p>检测到会话丢失或未登录状态</p>
            </div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="server-match <%= serverMatches ? 'server-match--yes' : 'server-match--no' %>">
            <% if (serverMatches) { %>
                <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'check', size: 20 }) %>
                <strong>服务器匹配:</strong> 请求路由到同一服务器
            <% } else { %>
                <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'alert-triangle', size: 20 }) %>
                <strong>服务器不匹配:</strong> 请求被路由到不同服务器
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <div class="info-grid info-grid--wide">
            <div class="info-section">
                <div class="section-title">
                    <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'key', size: 16 }) %>
                    会话信息
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">JSESSIONID</div>
                    <div class="info-value"><%= sessionId %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">登录用户</div>
                    <div class="info-value"><%= username || '未登录' %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">登录时间</div>
                    <div class="info-value"><%= loginTime || '未登录' %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">会话状态</div>
                    <div class="info-value <%= sessionPersistent ? 'info-value--ok' : 'info-value--down' %>">
                        <% if (sessionPersistent) { %>
                            <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'check', size: 13 }) %> 活跃
                        <% } else { %>
                            <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'x', size: 13 }) %> 无效
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-section">
                <div class="section-title">
                    <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'server', size: 16 }) %>
                    服务器信息
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">当前服务器IP</div>
                    <div class="info-value"><%= currentServer %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">会话创建服务器IP</div>
                    <div class="info-value"><%= sessionServer || '未知' %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">服务器匹配</div>
                    <div class="info-value <%= serverMatches ? 'info-value--ok' : 'info-value--down' %>">
                        <% if (serverMatches) { %>
                            <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'check', size: 13 }) %> 匹配
                        <% } else { %>
                            <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'x', size: 13 }) %> 不匹配
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">当前时间</div>
                    <div class="info-value live-clock"><%= currentTime %></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-section">
                <div class="section-title">
                    <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'globe', size: 16 }) %>
                    网络信息
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">客户端IP</div>
                    <div class="info-value"><%= clientIP %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">X-Forwarded-For</div>
                    <div class="info-value"><%= headers['x-forwarded-for'] || '未设置' %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">X-Real-IP</div>
                    <div class="info-value"><%= headers['x-real-ip'] || '未设置' %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">User-Agent</div>
                    <div class="info-value ua-value"><%= headers['user-agent'] %></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-section">
                <div class="section-title">
                    <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'cookie', size: 16 }) %>
                    Cookie信息
                </div>
                <% if (Object.keys(cookies).length > 0) { %>
                    <% Object.entries(cookies).forEach(([key, value]) => { %>
                        <div class="info-item">
                            <div class="info-label"><%= key %></div>
                            <div class="info-value"><%= value %></div>
                        </div>
                    <% }) %>
                <% } else { %>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="info-value text-muted">无其他Cookie</div>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-xl">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="location.reload()">
                <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'refresh-cw', size: 14 }) %>
                刷新测试
            </button>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">
                <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'home', size: 14 }) %>
                返回主页
            </a>
            <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-danger">
                <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'log-out', size: 14 }) %>
                退出登录
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="help-block">
            <h4>会话保持判断依据</h4>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>JSESSIONID 持久性</strong> 多次请求中会话ID保持一致</li>
                <li><strong>服务器路由</strong> 检查请求是否路由到相同的后端服务器</li>
                <li><strong>会话数据完整性</strong> 登录信息和会话数据是否完整保存</li>
                <li><strong>Cookie 传递</strong> 会话Cookie是否正确传递和识别</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>负载均衡测试建议</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>多次刷新此页面，观察服务器IP是否变化</li>
                <li>如果启用了会话粘性，服务器IP应保持一致</li>
                <li>如果没有会话粘性，但会话保持正常，说明会话共享配置正确</li>
                <li>观察 X-Forwarded-For 等负载均衡器添加的头部信息</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/clock.js"></script>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
